4/5 Like many of you, Iâ€™d wake up, dress my best, put on a smile and drive to work overtime in a job that could honestly care less about me. It was my daily routine, and it was slowly but surely driving me insane. I look at this ape, and imagine that he's been through the same...

3/5 Fast forward to 2 weeks ago, when @dt_chain purchased BAYC #2655 off the floor for 104 ETH. The Steve Jobs-esque wool turtleneck, the crazy eyes, and the dumbfounded mouth. This ape struck a chord with me. It shares a story so similar to my own that it's almost comical...

2/5 Picture this, in 2020, I would break a sweat after every debit card swipe. Watching that loading icon go around and around just hoping that my transaction would finish and say "approved". Now here I am 2 years later, doing the same, but this time for a $275,000 purchase.
